---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About" description="About FeatureSignals — an open-source feature management platform by Vivekananda Technology Labs.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="inline-block rounded-full bg-indigo-50 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-indigo-700 mb-6 ring-1 ring-indigo-100">
        About Us
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">About FeatureSignals</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        The feature management platform built for developers who want control, transparency, and zero vendor lock-in.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 sm:mt-16 space-y-10">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Who we are</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          <strong class="text-slate-800">FeatureSignals</strong> is a product of <strong class="text-slate-800">Vivekananda Technology Labs</strong>.
          We build open-source developer tools focused on feature management, experimentation, and safe software delivery.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">What we do</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          FeatureSignals is an open-source <strong class="text-slate-800">feature flag and feature management platform</strong>. It enables engineering
          teams to control feature rollouts, run A/B experiments, and manage configurations in real time — without expensive SaaS contracts.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-sm">Feature Flags</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">Boolean, string, number, JSON, and A/B flag types with targeting rules and percentage rollouts.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-sm">A/B Experimentation</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">Consistent hashing, weighted splits, mutual exclusion groups, and impression tracking.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-sm">SDKs for Every Stack</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">Go, Node.js, Python, Java, C#, Ruby, React, and Vue with OpenFeature providers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 p-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-sm">Self-Hosted</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">Apache-2.0 licensed. Deploy with Docker Compose, Kubernetes, or a single Go binary.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Pricing</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          We offer a <strong class="text-slate-800">Free</strong> plan, a <strong class="text-slate-800">Pro</strong> plan at
          <strong class="text-slate-800">&#8377;999/month</strong>, and an <strong class="text-slate-800">Enterprise</strong> plan
          with custom pricing. All plans include the full feature set. See our <a href="/pricing" class="font-medium text-indigo-600 underline decoration-indigo-200 hover:text-indigo-700">Pricing page</a> for details.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Business Details</h2>
        <dl class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm">
          <div>
            <dt class="font-semibold text-slate-700">Legal Name</dt>
            <dd class="mt-0.5 text-slate-600">Vivekananda Technology Labs</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="font-semibold text-slate-700">Trade Name</dt>
            <dd class="mt-0.5 text-slate-600">FeatureSignals</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="font-semibold text-slate-700">Registered Address</dt>
            <dd class="mt-0.5 text-slate-600">Flat no 308, L5-Block, LIG, Chitrapuri Colony, Manikonda, Hyderabad, Telangana - 500089, India</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="font-semibold text-slate-700">Contact</dt>
            <dd class="mt-0.5 text-slate-600"><a href="mailto:support@featuresignals.com" class="font-medium text-indigo-600 underline decoration-indigo-200 hover:text-indigo-700">support@featuresignals.com</a></dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="font-semibold text-slate-700">Nature of Business</dt>
            <dd class="mt-0.5 text-slate-600">IT Services — Cloud-hosted software, APIs, SDKs, and developer tools for feature management.</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center pt-4">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4">Questions? We'd love to hear from you.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <a href="mailto:support@featuresignals.com" class="rounded-lg border border-slate-300 px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 hover:border-slate-400">Contact Us</a>
          <a href="/" class="rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white transition-all hover:bg-indigo-700 hover:shadow-md">Back to Home</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
